Class CategoryManagerImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CategoryManager

    @ApplicationScoped
 @CategoryManagerDB
public class CategoryManagerImpl
extends GenericManagerImpl
implements CategoryManager
    Category manager class.

    This class is used to manage categories according to the business logic. It should be used by the controllers to handle categories like adding, deleting and so. The access of one of data access object method by the controllers is strictly forbidden.

    See Also:
    add(String), find(String), update(Category, HashMap), delete(Category), delete(long)
